0.1.0.name: wordpress/simple-youtube-search-include-by-gopsdepth
0.1.0.description:
Overview

Simple youtube search include plug-in is a short-code plug-in that will help you add youtube video with search terms.

How to use

At Version 1.0.0, I have 2 ways you can choose.

  1. Simple to use, you just add this short-code
[f2c_youtube_inc s="search terms" static="no"]

*** 's' attribute is required attribute.* *** 'static="no"' value will force plugin don't update a youtube video on your post, that's mean it will be get new one every time.

  1. Use F2C Youtube buttons to add short-code.

Attributes

s => search terms. Required. eg. s="batman return"

static => indicate a static youtube video. Set "no" only for non-static youtube video. Default is 'yes'. eg. static="no"

output => indicate an output. "shortcode" is youtube video or "url" is link string. Default is 'sho
